    - answer: "\xC4\xE4net ja musiikki"
      englishAnswer: Music and sounds
      color: {r: 1, g: 0.6313726, b: 0, a: 1}
    - answer: Tarina
      englishAnswer: Story
      color: {r: 1, g: 0.6313726, b: 0, a: 1}
    - answer: Pelattavuus
      englishAnswer: Playability
      color: {r: 1, g: 0.6313726, b: 0, a: 1}
    - answer: Pelaajan valinnat
      englishAnswer: Player's choices
      color: {r: 1, g: 0.6313726, b: 0, a: 1}
    - answer: Tunnelma
      englishAnswer: Atmosphere
      color: {r: 1, g: 0.6313726, b: 0, a: 1}
  - question: Voiko peli olla taidetta, vaikka se ei olisi visuaalisesti kaunis?
    englishQuestion: 
    answers:
    - answer: "Kyll\xE4"
      englishAnswer: Yes
      color: {r: 0.08627451, g: 0.8901961, b: 0.21568628, a: 1}
    - answer: Ei
      englishAnswer: No
      color: {r: 1, g: 0.27450982, b: 0.27450982, a: 1}
  - question: "Oletko joskus pelannut peli\xE4, joka on her\xE4tt\xE4nyt sinussa
